functionDecorators.name: getPopulatedTicksInWord
functionDecorators.description: Get all the tick data for the populated ticks from a word of the tick bitmap of a pool.

parameterDecorators.name: pool
parameterDecorators.description: The address of the pool for which to fetch populated tick data.

parameterDecorators.name: tickBitmapIndex
parameterDecorators.description: The index of the word in the tick bitmap for which to parse the bitmap and fetch all the populated ticks.

returnDecorators.name: populatedTicks
returnDecorators.description: An array of tick data for the given word in the tick bitmap.
